      <title>苹果失去了另一位顶级设计师，延续了乔尼·伊夫离开后的局面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/apple-loses-another-top-designer-extending-post-jony-ive-exodus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔尼·艾维 (Jony Ive) 领导下的苹果公司设计团队的撤离现已接近完成，这是一支传奇团队，帮助该公司开拓了音乐播放器、智能手机、平板电脑和智能手表。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/apple-loses-another-top-designer-extending-post-jony-ive-exodus</guid>
